attributes.title: Join Us For A Bite (Remastered)
attributes.caption: The biggest song on our channel is 5 years old today!!! And so naturally, we wanted to remaster and revisit the song and video. Big shout out to Harry101UK for animating this amazing video! And of course, a big thank you to the wickedly talented, Andrea Storm Kaden for her vocals!
attributes.description: The biggest song on our channel is 5 years old today!!! And so naturally, we wanted to remaster and revisit the song and video. Big shout out to Harry101UK for animating this amazing video! And of course, a big thank you to the wickedly talented, Andrea Storm Kaden for her vocals!

attributes.title: "Back for Another Bite"
attributes.caption: This was a special project for us. We wanted to pay homage not only to the game series itself but also to all the songs we've done about FNAF. It was loads of fun bringing it back to the first game and building the security office in our own studio. Big shout out to  @DaRegularSauce  and their suit, which brought the video to life! And then thanks to our crew who brought it even more to life. Enjoy our new FNAF Rap, "Back for Another Bite"!
